      "note": "Redesign 2026 baseline: brand (Indigo), accent (Orange), success (Emerald), warning (Amber), error (Rose), info (Sky), neutral (Slate); full type ramp; 4px spacing grid; radius sm=6; slate-tinted shadow scale."
    }
  ],
